==English==

===Noun===
'''almond''' (plural: [[almonds]])

#<!--DefA-->A type of tree [[nut]].
#<!--DefB-->The [[tree]] that produces almonds.
#<!--DefC-->(colour) The colour of the [[kernel]] of an almond without its shell and thin seed coat, a creamy off-white colour.

